snippet.title: Empire Earth Gold Edition | Intro Trailer [GOG]
snippet.description:
✅ Link to the game 👉  https://bit.ly/3zqWkMs

Control the destiny of a fledgling civilization through as many as 500,000 years of human history. From humble beginnings, you must exploit the natural resources around you to build an empire capable of dominating the Earth. But your rise to supremacy will not go unchallenged. As was the case throughout history, rival civilizations are certain to oppose you every step of the way.
